      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust Nissan 300ZX Twin Turbo featuring the iconic VG30DETT power plant. This Z32 retains its factory Garrett T22 turbochargers, delivering consistent boost through the original dual-intercooler setup. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 5-speed manual transmission and a viscous limited-slip differential (VLSD), ensuring exceptional power transfer to the rear wheels. This example features a fully operational Super HICAS four-wheel steering system, providing superior lateral stability. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive timing belt service and a pressurized intake tract leak test to ensure peak volumetric efficiency. While the exterior shows minor age-appropriate patina, the chassis remains rigid and the compression across all six cylinders is within factory specifications.",
